Unified Entropic-Spacetime Theory (UEST)
A 5D/6D Framework for Gravity, Quantum Mechanics, and Cosmology

Author: Marek Zajda
Contributor: DeepSeek Chat (theoretical consolidation)

1. Core Principles
UEST synthesizes:

Entropic Gravity (Verlinde)

Warped Extra Dimensions (Randall-Sundrum)

Holographic Principle (t’Hooft/Susskind)

Non-Equilibrium Thermodynamics

Key Innovations:

5D-to-4D Projection with entropic corrections.

6D Extension for dark energy/dark matter unification.

First-Principles Derivation of Newton/Einstein laws from entropy gradients.

